msgid "# Dynamic Chunked Pipeline Parallel"
msgstr "# 动态分块流水线并行"

msgid "## Overview"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid "### When to Use"
msgstr "### 使用场景"

msgid ""
"- **Variable-length sequence serving**: PP does not introduce degradation on short sequences, and gains benefits through dynamic chunks on long sequences.\n"
"- **Ultra-long sequence inference**: For sequences exceeding single-machine memory capacity (e.g., 1M tokens), dynamic chunking significantly reduces pipeline idle time."
msgstr ""
"- **变长序列服务**：PP 在短序列上不会引入性能退化，并通过动态分块在长序列上获得收益。\n"
"- **超长序列推理**：对于超出单机内存容量的序列（例如 100 万 token），动态分块可显著减少流水线空闲时间。"

msgid "## Supported Scenarios"
msgstr "## 支持场景"

msgid "## How to Enable"
msgstr "## 启用方法"

msgid "### Online Serving"
msgstr "### 在线服务"

msgid "### Offline Inference"
msgstr "### 离线推理"

msgid "## Configuration Parameters"
msgstr "## 配置参数"

msgid "### Parameter Tuning"
msgstr "### 参数调优"

msgid ""
"- `smooth_factor`: Controls trust level in dynamic prediction\n"
"    - `1.0`: Strictly follow model prediction\n"
"    - `0.6~0.85`: Balance dynamic adjustment and scheduling overhead\n"
"    - `0.0`: No dynamic adjustment (degrades to fixed chunking)\n"
"- `min_chunk`: Generally doesn't need adjustment. Should be smaller than `max-num-batched-tokens`"
msgstr ""
"- `smooth_factor`：控制对动态预测的信任程度\n"
"    - `1.0`：严格遵循模型预测\n"
"    - `0.6~0.85`：平衡动态调整与调度开销\n"
"    - `0.0`：无动态调整（退化为固定分块）\n"
"- `min_chunk`：通常无需调整。应小于 `max-num-batched-tokens`"

msgid "## Recommended Settings"
msgstr "## 推荐设置"

msgid "### max-num-batched-tokens"
msgstr "### max-num-batched-tokens"

msgid "### Online Calibration"
msgstr "### 在线校准"

msgid ""
"1. Modify "
"`<YOUR_AISBENCH_PATH>/benchmark/ais_bench/datasets/synthetic/synthetic_config.py`:"
msgstr ""
