"`<YOUR_AISBENCH_PATH>/benchmark/ais_bench/datasets/synthetic/synthetic_config.py`："

msgid "2. Run for online calibration:"
msgstr "2. 运行在线校准："

msgid "## Performance"
msgstr "## 性能"

msgid "- Qwen3-235B:"
msgstr "- Qwen3-235B："

msgid "## Constraints"
msgstr "## 约束条件"

msgid ""
"- **Pipeline Parallelism Required**: `--pipeline-parallel-size > 1`\n"
"- **Chunked Prefill Required**: `--enable-chunked-prefill`\n"
"- **Incompatible with Balance Scheduling**: Cannot enable `VLLM_ASCEND_BALANCE_SCHEDULING`\n"
"- **Startup Overhead**: Profiling adds ~64 forward passes (tens of seconds)"
msgstr ""
"- **需要流水线并行**：`--pipeline-parallel-size > 1`\n"
"- **需要分块预填充**：`--enable-chunked-prefill`\n"
"- **与均衡调度不兼容**：不能启用 `VLLM_ASCEND_BALANCE_SCHEDULING`\n"
"- **启动开销**：性能分析会增加约 64 次前向传播（数十秒）"

